    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just hard to hold onto the struggle when even the struggle feels fake. like you said, if it's all just a futile thing, then why does everyone act like there's some big prize at the end? why is there so much pressure to keep fighting just to exist for a second longer?",
